  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">h</span> Početni se izgovara disanjem vazduha kroz grlo, stvarajući blag zvučni trenje.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">h</span> prati finalne <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ha</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">he</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">hu</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">he</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">hē</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">喝</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">hé</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">合</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">hè</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">褐</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
